2.4.4
- Fixed ender effect particles making a pillar.
- Implemented a new internal message API.
- Renamed a few configs and storage keys.
- Changes in configs across versions are updated (new configs loaded, old configs removed.)
- If an effect item despawns or is destroyed, it can be crafted again.
- Fixed the way apophis applies skins and nametags (it works on rejoin now).
- Fixed invis death messages so they apply if the player has the infuse effect, not the potion effect.
- Redid the action bar code.  It stays centered now.
- Fixed an issue with the ender effect whining in console about an event.
- Thief effect actually hides people from tablist
- Effect-based item enchantments get reverted to their original levels when stashed or dropped.
- Cooldown timers don't start until after the spark ends. (Technically they do start but they're offset by the duration timer)
- Added custom events for equipping and unequipping effects
- The hit tracker's decay rate is now configurable.  Check the config.yml for more info
- Thunder effect is accurate now
- Fixed an issue with the hit tracker where hit counts were counted wrong.
- Fixed /cleareffects
- Made dropped heads match the player they drop from